>> time required: 1 hours
>> course: banchan

Dice @cucumber{1} put in bowl with salt, let sit, strain and remove excess water
Hardboil @eggs{4} and separate white from yellow, dice white
Peel, chop and rinse @russet potatoes{1%kg} into 2cm slices
Put potatoes in pan cover with water and salt, cook ~{20%minutes}
Remove water and simmer potatoes to remove excess water
Mash potatoes with egg yolks
Add egg whites, cucumber, @white pepper{0.5%tsp}, and @sugar{4%tbsp}
Add @mayonnaise{1%cup} and mix well
Serve room temp or chilled
